x4freetext: Synchrocyclotron neutron velocity
spectrometer.
200-m flight path. The overall time resolution
was 0.5 ns/m at the highest energy.
Translated from SCISRS.
Converted to reaction formalism.
BP: Updated to new date formats, lower
case. Corrections according last EXFOR rules and
Dict. Deleted subentries 8,9,10,11,12,13 (unobtainable
data) per an NRDC decision for data sets that were
published before 2000 (C32 of WP2022-01). Added mean
observed level spacing (D).
From the observed cross sections and the
shapes of resonances it has been possible to assign
the L and J values to some of the levels.
